Instalation guide CellGPU on ubuntu:

CGAL (latest version):

- sudo apt-get install libcgal-dev

NetCDF-4 C++ (latest version):

- Intall NetCDF-4 C first: sudo apt-get install libnetcdf-dev

- Install netcdf c++ legacy version using: sudo apt install libnetcdf-cxx-legacy-dev

Eighen (latest version):

- sudo apt-get install libeigen3-dev

CUDA (latest version):

- wget https://developer.download.nvidia.com/compute/cuda/11.1.0/local_installers/cuda_11.1.0_455.23.05_linux.run

- sudo sh cuda_11.1.0_455.23.05_linux.run
